# OpenRouter API key (https://openrouter.ai/keys).
# Copy this file to ".env" and paste your key after the '=' sign.
# The .env file is git-ignored and is never shared.
#
# Only the screening, extraction and synthesis stages call an LLM (through OpenRouter);
# indexing and raw retrieval run offline with a local embedding model and need no key.
# A free OpenRouter account works, and OpenRouter offers free and low-cost models
# (set LLM_MODEL in config.py or override it per API request), so the full pipeline
# can be exercised end to end at little or no cost.
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
